<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="seek-v">seek <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /siːk/    美 /siːk/  </p>
<p>(sought, sought) [正式用语或书面用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>寻找</strong></h4>
<p>to look for sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>seek jobs / work / employment 
找工作；求职</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a job-seeking guide 
求职指南</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>sought for</strong> a place to shelter from the rain, but in vain. 
他们寻找避雨的地方，但没能找到。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>寻求；谋求</strong></h4>
<p>to try to get sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>seek one’s fortune</strong> 
寻找出路；寻找致富之路</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book inspires confidence in students who wish to seek their own answers.
这本书使那些想寻求自己的答案的学生产生自信心。</p><footer>2014 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To care for wisdom and truth and improvement of the soul is far better than to seek money and honor and reputation.  
注重智慧、真理和灵魂进步远比追求金钱、荣誉和名声要好得多。</p><footer>——苏格拉底</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>征求 (建议、意见等)；请求 (帮助、援助等)</strong></h4>
<p>to ask sb for sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>seek ( sb’s ) advice</strong>
征求(某人的)建议</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>seek ( sb’s ) help</strong> / <strong>assistance</strong>
请求(某人的)帮助</p></div>

<h4 id="4-attempt">4.<strong>试图；企图 (attempt)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>seek to do sth (try to do sth):</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Scientists have been seeking to understand the mystery of the “sixth sense” of direction.
科学家一直在试图解开方向的第六感之谜。</p><footer>2010 江苏</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="seek-out">seek out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>找出；找到：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must seek out a solution to the problem. 
我们必须找到解决问题的办法。</p></div></div>